      <title>生物科技亿万富翁黄颂雄因 ImmunityBio 股票变动被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/biotech-billionaire-soon-shiong-sued-over-immunitybio-stock-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[生物科技亿万富翁黄松雄 (Patrick Soon-Shiong) 在一场股东诉讼中被指控误导 ImmunityBio Inc. 的投资者了解该公司旗舰抗癌药物的前景，以此来损害投资者的利益。]]></description>
